Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.86,0:00:05.48,Default2,,0,0,0,,These ladies and gentlemen are relatives of Kirari Momobami, the head of the main family.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.30,0:00:10.49,Default2,,0,0,0,,They are all part of the Momobami Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.50,0:00:10.49,Current Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(292,272)}Episode 2:\NThe Women of the\NMomobami Clan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:15.18,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Momobami Clan?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.86,0:00:16.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What on Earth...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:19.83,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'd like to thank you all for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:21.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,Drop the act.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:26.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,You announced that the winner of this election would become the next Momobami leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:31.13,Default2,,0,0,0,,So it's only natural that the adults would panic and send us as representatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.13,0:00:34.13,Default2,,0,0,0,,After inheriting the Momobami leadership,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:37.74,Default2,,0,0,0,,you quickly gained control over this academy as its student council president. {Curtis: added "council"}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.74,0:00:42.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,You centralized control over the debts and liabilities of both current and former students,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:46.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,exerting immense influence on the political and economic establishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:51.78,Default2,,0,0,0,,And so, the student council presidency at Hyakkao Academy has become a position of tremendous power.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:55.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,Control of this academy is control of the nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:01:00.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,And yet, you have chosen to abandon your position and wager it in an election.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.77,0:01:03.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,To make the winner leader of the clan, no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:07.88,Default2,,0,0,0,,{つまりこの選挙は、ひゃっかおう学園と桃喰一族　勝者総取りの跡目争い}Essentially, this election is a winner-take-all succession struggle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:10.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,{つまりこの選挙は、ひゃっかおう学園と桃喰一族　勝者総取りの跡目争い}for both Hyakkao Academy and the Momobami Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:17.87,Default2,,0,0,0,,Do you find it amusing, Kirari? Watching the branch families run helter-skelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:19.30,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yes, very much so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:23.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,I expected as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.27,0:01:26.65,Default2,,0,0,0,,You take what we all wanted with ease,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.65,0:01:30.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,and then you relinquish it and provide us with a chance to acquire it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:33.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,I have always...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:36.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,utterly despised you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.25,0:01:41.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:47.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't keep up. What's happening with the election? Momobami? Clan leadership?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.16,0:01:54.50,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one thing of which I'm certain is that our president's academy is on the verge of being devoured by this family!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.50,0:01:59.09,Default2,,0,0,0,,This is completely impermissible! All sense of order at the school will be lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:02.07,Default2,,0,0,0,,She is correct, President. Please reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.84,0:02:06.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,Well, if that's the president's decision, so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:13.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No use trying to stop her now. But if this interferes with my career, I'll crush her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:18.05,Default2,,0,0,0,,Sounds like fun! I'll give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:22.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,Not that any of these girls will be better than Yumeko, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:27.25,Default2,,0,0,0,,There's even a grade schooler!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:30.30,Default2,,0,0,0,,This is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:33.17,Default2,,0,0,0,,Calm yourself, Yuriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:37.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,If you want to preserve the status quo, then all you need to do is win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.93,0:02:39.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,Sayaka, the same goes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:42.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,The opportunity is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:46.43,Default2,,0,0,0,,After all, everyone has an equal shot in this election,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:50.19,Default2,,0,0,0,,and it will be decided with gambling alone.
