Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:20.62,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}Who will be first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:20.62,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}saisho wa dare? {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:24.04,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}Moderation is boring.
