Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.63,0:03:34.04,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}Let's have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.63,0:03:34.04,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}tanoshimimashou {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:45.73,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}It feels good when you indulge.
