Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:53.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}I'll live, live, live, live a story of wonderful thrills.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:53.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}suteki na suriru no sutoorii wo ikiru ikiru ikiru ikiru {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:04:00.62,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}We won't lose anything of importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:04:00.62,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}ushinau mono wa takaga shireteru {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:07.34,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}We may lose our tomorrow, but not our whole future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:07.34,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}ashita wo nakushitemo mirai ga nakunarutte wake janai {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:13.85,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}If you want to dream, you need to be world-weary.
