Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:45.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hello, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:49.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm the head of the Election Management Committee, Runa Yomotsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:51.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,Did you catch our poster?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:56.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm going to explain everything now, so pay attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:05:00.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,If you miss something, you might end up a house pet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:05.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,First and foremost! You won't be using ballots in this election.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.39,0:05:08.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,You can only make and receive votes through gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:11.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,Any other exchange of votes is prohibited.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:13.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,So, no need to announce your candidacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:18.25,Default2,,0,0,0,,Everyone is a voter, and everyone is a candidate! The election will run for 30 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:21.74,Default2,,0,0,0,,You can gamble however and with whomever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:26.26,Default2,,0,0,0,,The person with the most votes at the end of those 30 days is the winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:33.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,From this moment onward, the student council presidential election has begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:29.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,Well, everybody? Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:40.36,Default2,,0,0,0,,These are the chips, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:41.36,Default2,,0,0,0,,Looks like a toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:44.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,I see; each student gets one chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:49.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,Each chip is a single vote, and you can gamble with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:52.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,It's too bad we can't buy them with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.47,0:05:54.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,Right when I'd managed to save some up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:59.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,Manyuda transfered me everything he owed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:00.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,Take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:07.05,Default2,,0,0,0,,Three billion yen!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:14.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,I was all excited about using this money to gamble to my heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:19.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,Even with all that money, you haven't changed a bit, Yumeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:22.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hey, you shouldn't be flaunting that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:25.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,Never know what kind of morons you'll attract.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:26.86,Default2,,0,0,0,,Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.46,0:06:29.03,Default2,,0,0,0,,Stop with the hugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:34.25,Default2,,0,0,0,,You've got that three billion yen all figured, but what about the other prize you won?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:40.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,I have no need for a person's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:44.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1600)}If I can keep gambling, I'm satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:48.26,Default2,,0,0,0,,I transferred Manyuda's life to a suitable person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:54.21,Default2,,0,0,0,,Oh. Sumeragi, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:59.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,She must be happy about that. Seemed like she was pretty attached to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:00.65,Default2,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:02.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yumeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:08.03,Default2,,0,0,0,,I doubt your head will ever come down from the clouds, but let me give you some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.03,0:07:12.03,Default2,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't take this student council president election lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:18.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,Haven't you heard? A whole bunch of weirdos have transferred in just in time for the election.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:23.25,Default2,,0,0,0,,From what I've heard, they all have "bami" in their surnames.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.61,Default2,,0,0,0,,"Bami"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:27.30,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yes. Same as the president's name, Momobami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:32.09,Default2,,0,0,0,,There's no way that's a coincidence. You should really be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:37.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yumeko, your surname has "bami" in it too. \NDo you know anything about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:43.35,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hm... I suppose they could be distant relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:52.11,Default2,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what a massive school! Everything's so extravagant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:56.60,Default2,,0,0,0,,She's giving up both the academy and the family leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,Kirari sure is generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:01.44,Default2,,0,0,0,,You're not the rep, though, Ibara.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:05.87,Default2,,0,0,0,,Shut up, Yumi. I'm here to support him. Right, Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:07.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:11.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,So, whoever earns the most votes becomes student council president.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:14.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,It is an election, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:18.21,Default2,,0,0,0,,And that one winner becomes leader of the main family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:20.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,Erimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:25.48,Default2,,0,0,0,,Be that as it may, I do not recommend trying to eliminate us Clan members first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:30.36,Default2,,0,0,0,,Not only do you run the risk of a plan backfiring, you will be painting a target on your back for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:33.24,Default2,,0,0,0,,Should wait 'til there's fewer people in the running.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:35.50,Default2,,0,0,0,,And don't go telling us about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:38.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,I know that! I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:39.87,Default2,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:46.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,I hope you have not forgotten our pact. Until we topple Kirari, we will not fight each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:51.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,I will kill anyone who stands in my way. Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:56.20,Default2,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. We all understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:09:01.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,So, how should we handle the Jabami girl—Yumeko Jabami?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:04.16,Default2,,0,0,0,,Jabami? Is that a branch family?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:05.06,Default2,,0,0,0,,Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:10.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,Very well. Yumeko Jabami is the second-born daughter of House Jabami, a fringe branch family of the Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:16.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,Soon after transferring to Hyakkao Academy, she defeated five student council members by gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:19.65,Default2,,0,0,0,,That is the information I have gathered on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:21.29,Default2,,0,0,0,,Wow, she's impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:27.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,It may be a fringe family, but the fact remains that she is part of the Clan. Isn't that right, Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:29.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yes, Miss Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:31.84,Default2,,0,0,0,,Should we include her in our pact?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:38.09,Default2,,0,0,0,,That will not be necessary. You are free to engage or ignore her however you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:42.43,Default2,,0,0,0,,Oh? That means we can go after her, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:43.46,Default2,,0,0,0,,Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:45.19,Default2,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:53.44,Default2,,0,0,0,,They sure got started right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:56.99,Default2,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess these are just toys to most students.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:02.24,Default2,,0,0,0,,Not to the students at the bottom of the school's hierarchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:04.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,However small it may be,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:06.42,Default2,,0,0,0,,they still have a real chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:09.20,Default2,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do, Yumeko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:15.01,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm going to use my vote to gamble with the president, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:17.19,Default2,,0,0,0,,I figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.00,0:10:19.86,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:22.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,In that case, you'd better earn a lot of votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:25.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,You can't challenge her with just one or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:28.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:34.78,Default2,,0,0,0,,There's so much power in one of these votes that even a single one cannot be ignored...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.37,0:10:37.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,At least, that's one view!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:46.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yumeko's plans are a mystery to me, as always.\N Does she want to become student council president?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:49.17,Default2,,0,0,0,,What about you, Saotome?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:52.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,What are your plans for this election?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:54.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:00.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,Saotome?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:04.78,Default2,,0,0,0,,I don't know. And it's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:06.43,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:10.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,Did I say something to offend her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:11.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:15.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,You are Yumeko Jabami, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:22.50,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yes, I most certainly am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.83,0:11:26.84,Default2,,0,0,0,,I am here to invite you to an election match.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:29.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,To gamble? I gladly accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:34.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yumeko, you should be careful. This must be one of the transfer students that Saotome...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:37.49,Default2,,0,0,0,,Are you from the Clan as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.52,0:11:38.18,Default2,,0,0,0,,That—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:46.20,Default2,,0,0,0,,I apologize. My name is Rei Batsubami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:49.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,I am here to assist the ladies and gentlemen of the Momobami Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:52.85,Default2,,0,0,0,,Will you be gambling with me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:55.86,Default2,,0,0,0,,Will I be... gambling...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:12:00.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,Certainly not. Your opponent will be someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:03.24,Default2,,0,0,0,,I will guide you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.94,0:12:05.83,Default2,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:11.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yumeko! Boy, have I missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:12.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,It was Ikishima?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:17.32,Default2,,0,0,0,,She invited me! Told me I'd get to gamble with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:19.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:22.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,This is Miss Erimi Mushibami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:25.85,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mushibami? Then she  {\i0}is {\i1}one of them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:29.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,Miss Mushibami, thank you so much for inviting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:32.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,You're actually pretty great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:35.10,Default2,,0,0,0,,Sorry for calling you a grade schooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:43.15,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You will have the pleasure of being the first I eliminate, lowly underling. Alongside Yumeko Jabami, that is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:47.23,Default2,,0,0,0,,It appears all the players have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.23,0:12:49.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,I will now take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:54.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,I am Inaho Yamato from the Election Management Committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:58.46,Default2,,0,0,0,,I will be managing this game space.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:01.05,Default2,,0,0,0,,Why do we need a manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:04.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,Anywhere there is gambling, there must be a Committee member.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:07.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,Voting is strictly regulated, so it is necessary for a Committee member
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:10.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,to be present at all gambling sites until the election is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:14.33,Default2,,0,0,0,,Dammit, who cares? Let's get this show on the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:16.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,You've got something good for us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:19.07,Default2,,0,0,0,,I believe it will satisfy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:22.65,Default2,,0,0,0,,You're not going to turn tail, are you, Yumeko Jabami?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:26.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,Of course not! I'm excited to see how we will be gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:30.24,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hey, doesn't this put Yumeko at a huge disadvantage?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:34.33,Default2,,0,0,0,,Rest assured, you are free to decline after you hear the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:40.20,Default2,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. The game I've prepared is fair as fair can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:42.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:44.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Our jobs would be meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:47.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}She got me so hot and bothered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:04.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's your deal all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:09.74,Default2,,0,0,0,,Why would you start crying over a game you came up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:18.21,Default2,,0,0,0,,You can't just end it after teasing me this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:22.25,Default2,,0,0,0,,Shit! If this ends, how am I gonna get off!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:26.29,Default2,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.29,0:14:28.26,Default2,,0,0,0,,What? I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:35.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You think I'd let myself lose to an lowborn brat like you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:40.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,Now we're talking. Y'know, I might be into that kinda thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:48.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,How can you cut so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:15:01.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,Only three strings remain! Your turn, Miss Mushibami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:04.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:09.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we haven't gotten it yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.31,0:15:12.21,Default2,,0,0,0,,We've got some real shitty luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:16.60,Default2,,0,0,0,,Oh, but the longer it takes, the better the game, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:20.71,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the hell is with them? There's only three left.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:27.49,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is crazy. Will they really...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:24.36,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How can they keep their fingers in when the blade will fall within three turns? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:31.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}not pull their fingers out until the final string is cut?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:37.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just can't take it anymore. I can't...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:42.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,Miss Mushibami... I hardly think this could be the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:46.09,Default2,,0,0,0,,but you're not thinking of pulling your finger out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:52.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,torture is the Mushibami family business.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:49.59,Default2,,0,0,0,,You said it yourself—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:55.35,Default2,,0,0,0,,And you wanted to see how long we could last.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:59.59,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yeah, true! That's what you said!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:03.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,Since torture is your family business, this must be preaching to the choir,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:08.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,but this Finger-Cutting Guillotine causes fear to build up as the strings are cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:12.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,Nobody can endure the steadily increasing terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:18.74,Default2,,0,0,0,,It's a physiological reaction so powerful as to make anyone abandon their pride and convictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.69,0:16:21.21,Default2,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:25.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,Now we're at the essence of it! Now the fun truly begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:28.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,So, why are you dawdling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:33.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,Pick up those scissors, if you would be so kind, and make that terror real!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.25,0:16:38.86,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:44.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No human being could possibly keep their finger under the blade until the final string.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:49.43,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}House Mushibami's torture is infallible! If such a person really existed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:53.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My family... the Mushibami family business would be undermined!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.11,0:17:06.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,Looks to be another miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:15.18,Default2,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is good. Oh, this is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:19.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,You're great. I think you can take me all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:21.68,Default2,,0,0,0,,The move is yours, Miss Ikishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:25.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,I know. Let's all come together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:26.44,Default2,,0,0,0,, {\an8}{\i1}Freak.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:29.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyway, there are just two strings left.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:35.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The game will be decided within the next two turns.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:40.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll prove it! When it comes down to one string, you  {\i0}will{\i1} pull your fingers out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:41.83,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have to!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.53,0:17:46.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This inescapable terror... is the cornerstone of my family!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:49.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm in heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:52.09,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get it wrong! Keep this going until the last—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:09.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,Game over! As all the strings have been cut, we have a result!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:13.18,Default2,,0,0,0,,Miss Mushibami removed her finger, and is thus eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:18.13,Default2,,0,0,0,,Miss Ikishima cut two strings at once, in violation of the rules, and is thus disqualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:22.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,Accordingly, the winner is Miss Yumeko Jabami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:24.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,Miss Jabami earns two chips!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:29.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,The hell were you thinking, cutting two strings at once!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.53,0:18:33.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,Why the fuck did you design this thing to not cut off any fingers!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:39.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,I thought... I thought I could finally make it happen with Yumeko... But you screwed it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:41.35,Default2,,0,0,0,,Dammit! God fucking dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:44.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yumeko! Say something to this piece of crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:47.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,The only piece of crap here is you, Ikishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:51.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea what you did?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:57.15,Default2,,0,0,0,,W-what do you mean? I was sharing the risk with you guys, just like you told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:59.41,Default2,,0,0,0,,You cut two strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.01,0:19:06.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,Those one-in-twenty odds slowly increased over a stretch of happy accidents, eventually reaching one-in-two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:10.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,It was like a miracle brought by God himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:14.42,Default2,,0,0,0,,And at the end of it all, we reached the ultimate choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:18.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yet you trampled on that final moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.02,0:19:24.32,Default2,,0,0,0,,Even though we weren't scared at all by that stuff about amputation and inescapable terror...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:30.42,Default2,,0,0,0,,Never show your face to me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:32.06,Default2,,0,0,0,,You disgust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:36.03,Default2,,0,0,0,,W-wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:38.65,Default2,,0,0,0,,Why... why is the iron plate still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:41.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,Didn't the dealer say she removed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:44.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,That was just a bit of insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:50.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,After hearing the rules, I thought it would be unfortunate if the device contained something like that iron plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:55.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, there was also a rattle to the table the guillotine is on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:20:01.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,But we were able to play the game without any difficulty, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:07.06,Default2,,0,0,0,,That was thanks to the dealer, Miss Yamato. She removed the pads from the table feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:11.15,Default2,,0,0,0,,Indeed! One of the pads was damaged,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:13.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,so I removed them all to ensure the table was balanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:17.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that you misinterpreted my words.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:20.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,But I wanted you to feel what we were feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.01,0:20:24.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why... that's why I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:28.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,Miss Mushibami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:34.21,Default2,,0,0,0,,The pride and conviction you showed us at the end were truly magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.24,0:20:38.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,Let's have fun gambling again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.35,0:20:48.60,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yumeko Jabami. This girl is part of the Momobami Clan, no doubt about it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:52.23,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I have no doubt either that our clan{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:54.48,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}will consume itself at this academy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:20:59.23,Default2,,0,0,0,,How long has it been since we had a casual conversation, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:02.11,Default2,,0,0,0,,Terano... Yumi. I hope you two are well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:06.10,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm doing great! That's all I've got going for me, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:09.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,The Clan would never come together like this under other circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:15.86,Default2,,0,0,0,,Quite right. However, I was a bit surprised to see you had brought Rei along as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:21.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,This school is your territory. Who would be foolish enough to waltz in without some insurance?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:27.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,But can {\i1}they{\i0}  really be counted on as insurance? House Batsubami was expelled from the Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:32.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,They are outcasts. I hardly think they would work on your behalf, even out of malice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:35.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't work on your behalf, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.46,0:21:39.22,Default2,,0,0,0,,That's what's good about 'em. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.22,0:21:41.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,An ill-conceived scheme would simply dig my own grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:45.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,I have merely thrown in a joker whose actions will be unpredictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:47.41,Default2,,0,0,0,,Nothing more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:54.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,How interesting. I've always liked that about you, Terano.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.00,0:21:55.78,Default2,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.78,0:21:58.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,At any rate, the game is already afoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.09,0:22:03.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,There can be no stopping it. This academy will fall to ruin, just as you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.14,0:22:09.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,Miss Yuriko! Miss Yuriko! Won't someone... please...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.89,0:22:19.09,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is so stupid.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.06,0:22:25.78,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{こんなこと考えてる時点で、あの女の手のひら...}Everyone's still dancing in the palm of that girl's hand...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.66,0:22:33.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,You're... the president? No, the vice president?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.25,0:22:42.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,You are Mary Saotome, correct? I've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.55,0:22:45.63,Default2,,0,0,0,,We have matters to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.40,0:23:12.10,ED,,0,0,0,,If you desire it so much as to writhe, I will give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.40,0:23:12.10,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}notautsu hodo ni motomeru no nara ataeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.10,0:23:16.35,ED,,0,0,0,,You will need to avail yourself of even your despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.10,0:23:16.35,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}zetsubou sae kate ni shite shimau
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.35,0:23:19.67,ED,,0,0,0,,Now, come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.35,0:23:19.67,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}saa oide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.67,0:23:25.82,ED,,0,0,0,,If you offer your body and soul, I will answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.67,0:23:25.82,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}mi mo kokoro mademo sashidasu nara kotaeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:31.42,ED,,0,0,0,,Tragedy will be overwhelmed by pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:31.42,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}higeki mo etsuraku ni nomareru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.42,0:23:39.07,ED,,0,0,0,,Consumed by an excess of pure carnal desire,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.42,0:23:39.07,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}amari nimo sekirara na retsujou ni ukasarenagara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.07,0:23:46.96,ED,,0,0,0,,Eventually you will live wishing only for a moment of titillation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.07,0:23:46.96,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}yagate shibireru youna shunkan dake wo negai ikiru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.08,0:23:55.17,ED,,0,0,0,,O soul that burns with desire, raise your glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.08,0:23:55.17,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}aa katsubou suru tamashii yo sakazuki wo kakage
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.17,0:24:01.94,ED,,0,0,0,,Sing an ode to such joy as will break you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.17,0:24:01.94,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kowareru hodo kanki no uta wo utaou
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.94,0:24:08.71,ED,,0,0,0,,Simple acclaim will never satisfy your cravings.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.94,0:24:08.71,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kassai dewa michitaru hazu mo nai uzuki
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.71,0:24:15.64,ED,,0,0,0,,It's maddening enough to bet on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.71,0:24:15.64,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kakeru hodo kuruoshii
